dct_title_s: Eastern Turkey in Asia. Sheet 47. Rijm el-Kheil / compiled for the Geographical Section, General Staff, by Lieut. Col. F.R. Maunsell, C.M.G. (raster)
dct_description_sm: Shows Rujm el-Hiri monument. "Drawn and printed at the War Office, May 1917." Relief shown by form lines and by spot heights. Includes an index to adjoining sheets, and a glossary.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. Intelligence Division
